ARTICLE 4

OBLIGATIONS OF PARTIES

(1)

RSA shall, in addition to facilitating the cooperation through the

ARC, provide administrative support to researchers and companies related to researcher's projects, and more specifically— coordinate the programme by bringing all the role players together;

avail the ARC research equipment and infrastructure for the F'SAGRI

Programme;

provide research expertise;

provide linkages with industry and farmers to enable (i)

coordination of the development of curricular for training programmes as per industry needs, through university and industry linkages; and (ii)

the provision of support and analysis of needs and the development of new training programmes;

be responsible for the formulation of a management framework for innovation, technology transfer processes and the management of intellectual property;

be responsible for resource mobilisation for training of farmers and extension personnel;

be responsible for the extension of services linkages between research and development;
